{"word":"γηροβοσκέω","slug":"γηροβοσκέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γηροβοσκέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:γηροβοσκός'><el>γηροβοσκός</el></a>\n<p/><i>to feed</i> or <i>tend in old age</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be so cherished</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}